OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with spells of rain
OL,6,Facross Scotland and Northern Ireland
OL,7,Ftoday, with the rain moving into parts
OL,8,Fof western England and Wales
OL,9,Fthroughout the afternoon. Elsewhere,
OL,10,Fearly fog clearing leading to a very
OL,11,Fmild day with spells of sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain in the west
OL,14,Fmoving a little further east
OL,15,Fovernight, although some eastern and
OL,16,Fsoutheastern areas remaining dry. Some
OL,17,Fclearer spells arriving into the
OL,18,Fnorthwest later. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
