OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright start in the east,
OL,6,Fotherwise generally rather cloudy with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain. The rain turning
OL,8,Fheavier and more persistent later in
OL,9,Fthe west. Brisk winds but staying mild.
